1.0.0.name: wordpress/fx-hey-counter
1.0.0.description:
Plugin displays visitors counter from hey.lt site. No need to insert code, jus simply activate plugin and you will have widget.

All you need is set your hey.lt ID in widget. Get your ID at http://www.hey.lt site and start counting your visitors.
